- https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bézier_curve
- Quadratic:
  - http://blog.gludion.com/2009/08/distance-to-quadratic-bezier-curve.html
  - http://stackoverflow.com/questions/6824452/nearest-point-on-a-quadratic-bezier-curve#6824647
- Cubic:
  - http://www.tinaja.com/glib/cmindist.pdf
  - http://web.archive.org/web/20161021130752/http://cagd.cs.byu.edu/~557/text/ch17.pdf
